originalText.text: We have an extremely busy sandwich shop in Brooklyn. It is not unusual for us to go through 1000 take out menus in a week. Menu Printing of NY at 1-800 – Printing keeps up with our demand without missing a beat. We have never run out of menu’s thank to the great service they provide.

originalText.text: Our chef changes the menu of our restaurant seasonally and sometimes more. When he needs new menu’s printed he orders them from Menu Printing in NY. We have been very satisfied with the menu printing service.
